## Warehouse KPI Monitoring â€“ Microsoft Fabric

### Context
Centralized KPI monitoring dashboard built in Microsoft Fabric to track daily warehouse performance indicators across multiple Power BI reports.

The dashboard consolidates operational KPIs into a single control panel used for daily management, deviation detection, and action prioritization.

### Business Purpose
- Daily operational follow-up of critical warehouse KPIs
- Early detection of indicators out of target
- Support daily management meetings and corrective actions
- Provide a single source of truth for operational performance

### KPIs Monitored
- Picking error rate vs picked units
- Picking errors
- ABC adherence
- Warehouse occupancy
- Breakage (picking and DU)
- Cycle time
- Container / packaging classification

Each KPI includes:
- Current value vs target
- Status (On Target / At Risk / Out of Target)
- Trend visualization
- Daily variation

### Tools
- Microsoft Fabric
- Power BI
- DAX

### Outcome
This dashboard enables warehouse leaders to monitor performance daily, quickly identify deviations, and focus operational actions on KPIs that are out of target.
